<arggraph id="micro_c081" topic_id="veganism_helps_environment" stance="pro">
  <edu id="e1"><![CDATA[Being a vegetarian or vegan helps the environment]]></edu>
  <edu id="e2"><![CDATA[by using less resources.]]></edu>
  <edu id="e3"><![CDATA[For example, the production of meat use more resources in terms of cattle feed, energy, and human labor.]]></edu>
  <edu id="e4"><![CDATA[Harvesting  vegetables will reduce waste.]]></edu>
  <edu id="e5"><![CDATA[The proper crops will also feed more people.]]></edu>
  <edu id="e6"><![CDATA[However, being vegetarian requires more vigilance in terms of sufficient vitamins, which meat eaters need not concern.]]></edu>
  <edu id="e7"><![CDATA[Overall, being vegetarian is easier on the environment]]></edu>
  <edu id="e8"><![CDATA[because production of fruit, vegetables and grain relieve strain on resources]]></edu>
  <edu id="e9"><![CDATA[and is a healthier life style.]]></edu>
